 the home ministry to keep inmates in open jail and parole, form parole boards and make separate clusters of inmates based on their health status in a bid to allay virus transmission risk.","title":"Parliamentary committee directs government to live up standards in prison health","url":"http://english.ratopati.com/story/15021","video":[]}
